record.title: MEASURE PLACED ON THE CALENDAR--H.R. 391

speaking.paragraph: Madam President, it is my understanding that H.R. 391 is at the desk and is due for a second reading.

record.chair: The clerk will read the bill for the second time.

speaking.paragraph: I object to any further proceedings at this time.

record.chair: Objection is heard. The bill will be placed on the calendar.
